%h2 New Award

%div.hint_toggle
  About Awards...
%div.hint_text{:style => 'display: none;'}
  %p Participants with achievements can be recognized with an award or recognition mechanism to encourage and inspire other companies in the Local Network.

= form_for @submodel, builder: DefaultFormBuilder, :url => submodels_path, :html => {:multipart => true} do |form|
  = render :partial => form
  %ul{:class => "tools inline", :style => 'float: right;'}
    %li= link_to 'Cancel', return_url, :class => 'cancel_large'
    %li= form.submit 'Create', :class => 'button'
